sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Button } from "react-scroll"; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, ImgWrap, Img, } from "./InfoElements"; export const InfoSection = ({ lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headline, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ); };
